# NirSoft Password Recovery USB Collector — .gitignore
# https://www.nirsoft.net/password_recovery_tools.html

# --- Runtime outputs (regenerated on every collector run) ---
# Timestamp folders like results/20260721_212853/ created by collector.ps1
results/[0-9]*_[0-9]*/
# results/readme.txt is project documentation and is intentionally committed

# --- Diagnostic scratch ---
# Working area for probe scripts and intermediate logs created during development
results/_dryrun_cli_test/

# --- Backup / scratch directories ---
# .bkp/ mirrors the project for safety nets; do NOT version
.bkp/

# --- NirSoft downloaded archives ---
# tools/zip/ contains the all-in-one NirSoft password-tools archive that we
# extract NirSoft EXEs from. Re-downloadable, large, does not belong in git.
tools/zip/

# --- Backup files (safety net) ---
# Defensive: ignore any .bak / .BAK / .backup / .bkp files anywhere in the tree.
# (An already-tracked scripts/collector.ps1.BAK stays tracked; this rule only
# prevents ADDITIONAL such files from being staged.)
*.bak
*.BAK
*.backup
*.bkp

# --- OS / editor cruft ---
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store
*.swp
*~
.vs/
.idea/
